  onGameStart: "Step up, player. Let\u2019s see if you've got the moves."
  thinking:
  - "Hmmm... which one\u2019ll make me shine tonight?"
  - Let's see... gotta keep my edge.
  - "hmm\u2026 smooth moves only."
  - and a one, and a two...
  - this one will go without a hitch
